OL,3,CMandelson sought #500k payout after
OL,4,Csacking over Epstein links - but got
OL,5,C#75k
OL,7,FLord Peter Mandelson sought a #500k
OL,8,Fpayout after he was sacked as
OL,9,Fambassador to the US over his
OL,10,Frelationship with paedophile financier
OL,11,FJeffrey Epstein, a newly released
OL,12,Ftranche of documents has revealed.
OL,14,FThe files, released by the government
OL,15,Fon Wednesday, show Mandelson asked for
OL,16,F#547,201 severance pay, but ultimately
OL,17,Fagreed to #75,000.
OL,19,FThis is made up of a #40,330 payment
OL,20,Fin place of serving his notice and a
OL,21,Fseverance payment of #34,670.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
