CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773328290
OL,3,CMandelson sought #500k payout after
OL,4,Csacking over Epstein links - but got
OL,5,C#75k
OL,7,FThe information is part of 147 pages
OL,8,Fof documents relating to the vetting
OL,9,Fprocess of Lord Mandelson, who served
OL,10,Fas US ambassador from December 2024
OL,11,Funtil September 2025, when he was
OL,12,Fousted after the extent of his
OL,13,Ffriendship with Epstein was brought to
OL,14,Flight.
OL,16,FLast month, MPs ordered the release of
OL,17,Fthe papers and what the government
OL,18,Fknew about his links to Epstein.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
