OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773328290
OL,3,CMandelson sought #500k payout after
OL,4,Csacking over Epstein links - but got
OL,5,C#75k
OL,7,FSpeaking in the Commons on Wednesday,
OL,8,FCabinet minister Darren Jones said:
OL,9,F"The prime minister has taken
OL,10,Fresponsibility for Peter Mandelson's
OL,11,Fappointment as ambassador to the
OL,12,FUnited States.
OL,14,F"He has acknowledged it was a mistake
OL,15,Fand has apologised."
OL,17,F'Reputational risk'
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
