CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773328290
OL,3,CMandelson sought #500k payout after
OL,4,Csacking over Epstein links - but got
OL,5,C#75k
OL,7,FThe files include a "due diligence"
OL,8,Fdocument drawn up before Lord
OL,9,FMandelson's appointment to the
OL,10,FWashington role, which noted a series
OL,11,Fof reports detailing his links with
OL,12,FEpstein.
OL,14,FThe document noted that after Epstein
OL,15,Fwas first convicted of procuring an
OL,16,Funderage girl in 2008 "their
OL,17,Frelationship continued across 2009-
OL,18,F2011, beginning when Lord Mandelson
OL,19,Fwas business minister and continuing
OL,20,Fafter the end of the Labour
OL,21,Fgovernment".
