CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773328290
OL,3,CMandelson sought #500k payout after
OL,4,Csacking over Epstein links - but got
OL,5,C#75k
OL,7,FIt also noted that "Mandelson
OL,8,Freportedly stayed in Epstein's house
OL,9,Fwhile he was in jail in June 2009".
OL,11,FThe prime minister previously insisted
OL,12,Fthat Mandelson misled him during the
OL,13,Fvetting process and that he concealed
OL,14,Fthe true nature of his relationship
OL,15,Fwith Epstein.
OL,17,FThis is the first batch of documents
OL,18,Fto be released by the government.
OL,26,@oD@TOUqD@bO]
