OL,3,CMandelson sought #500k payout after
OL,4,Csacking over Epstein links - but got
OL,5,C#75k
OL,7,FSome are to be withheld for national
OL,8,Fsecurity or foreign relations reasons,
OL,9,Fand some will be released at a later
OL,10,Fdate to avoid interfering with the
OL,11,Fongoing police investigation into Lord
OL,12,FMandelson.
OL,14,FHe was arrested on February 23 on
OL,15,Fsuspicion of misconduct in public
OL,16,Foffice, having been accused of passing
OL,17,Fsensitive information on to Epstein
OL,18,Fduring his time as business secretary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
