OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773328290
OL,3,CMandelson sought #500k payout after
OL,4,Csacking over Epstein links - but got
OL,5,C#75k
OL,7,FHe was subsequently bailed, but later
OL,8,Freleased from his bail conditions,
OL,9,Falthough he remains under
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,FAfter his release on investigation,
OL,13,Flawyers representing Mandelson said:
OL,14,F"Peter Mandelson's overriding priority
OL,15,Fis to cooperate with the police
OL,16,Finvestigation, as he has done
OL,17,Fthroughout this process, and to clear
OL,18,Fhis name."
OL,20,FThis is a breaking news story. More to
OL,21,Ffollow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
